<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Digi Fest Event Page</title>

<style>

body{
    margin:0;
    font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;
    background-color:#f4f4f4;
}

/* header section */
.top-header{
    background-color:#12052a;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:25px;
}

.top-header h1{
    font-size:48px;
    margin:0;
}

/* navigation */
.menu{
    margin-top:10px;
}

.menu a{
    color:white;
    margin:0 12px;
    text-decoration:none;
    font-size:16px;
}

.menu a:hover{
    color:#ffd700;
}

/* page layout */
.container{
    max-width:1100px;
    margin:auto;
    display:flex;
    gap:20px;
    padding:20px;
}

/* left content */
.left-box{
    flex:2;
    background:white;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:8px;
}

/* right content */
.right-box{
    flex:1;
    background:#1c2f70;
    color:white;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:8px;
}

.right-box img{
    width:100%;
    margin-top:12px;
    border:4px solid white;
}

/* footer */
.bottom{
    background:#5e0fa3;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:15px;
    margin-top:20px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="top-header">
    <h1>DIGI FEST 2022</h1>

    <div class="menu">
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">About</a>
        <a href="#">Events</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
        <a href="#">Tickets</a>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container">

<div class="left-box">
<h2>Welcome to Digi Fest</h2>

<p>
Digi Fest is an exciting festival that celebrates technology, creativity,
and digital innovation in the city of Cardiff. This year’s theme focuses
on collaboration and learning new digital skills.
</p>

<p>
Visitors can explore different workshops, learn about web design,
and discover how technology is changing the world. The festival
is designed to be both educational and fun for everyone.
</p>

<img src="https://picsum.photos/id/1015/600/300" alt="Laptop with coding">
</div>

<div class="right-box">
<h2>Event Line-Up</h2>

<ul>
<li>Getting Started with HTML</li>
<li>Using Images and Links</li>
<li>Creating Page Layouts</li>
</ul>

<img src="https://picsum.photos/id/160/300/300" alt="Technology image">
<img src="https://picsum.photos/id/201/300/300" alt="Technology image">

</div>

</div>

<div class="bottom">
© 2022 Digi Fest | All Rights Reserved
</div>

</body>
</html>
